# Alpha Vantage API Key (untuk data crypto & forex real-time)
# Dapatkan gratis di: https://www.alphavantage.co/support/#api-key
# Digunakan untuk: Real-time price data, technical indicators
ALPHA_VANTAGE_API_KEY=your_alpha_vantage_api_key_here

# Twelve Data API Key (untuk data market premium)
# Dapatkan gratis di: https://twelvedata.com/
# Digunakan untuk: High-frequency price data, volume analysis
